# Production Checklist

## Before Deploy
- [ ] Remove or gate `console.log` of env vars and sensitive data (initFirebase.js)
- [ ] Tighten Firestore rules: per-collection, role-based; validate document shapes
- [ ] Ensure `.env` / `.env.local` are in `.gitignore`; use CI secrets for build
- [ ] Run `npm run build`; fix any build errors
- [ ] Verify all `REACT_APP_*` vars are set in deployment environment

## Firestore Rules
- Current: `allow read, write: if request.auth != null` (dev only)
- Production: Add rules per collection; restrict admin collections to `admin == true`
- Validate required fields and data types in rules

## Performance
- Lazy-load heavy screens if needed
- Ensure analytics does not block render
